{"tid":13893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【還我世界盃】樂視香港員工「被離職」 倖存員工：心慌慌中","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T09:23:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3855623ef2ef547f75c2f88d510f2c37aa8d09","tid":13893,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"市傳樂視裁員10%救亡，昨日樂視香港區已經有員工收到「離職邀請」，有樂視員工向本報稱，公司未開始派大信封，但裁員消息在同事間人傳人，搞到「心慌慌」！<br />\n<br />\n《明報》報道，有樂視香港員工被「邀請離職」，涉及最少8名銷售、物流部等部門的員工，有樂視香港的中層員工稱，部門主管暗示公司財困，人事部指據工作評核表現，要求他簽署由公司早已準備的辭職信，他拒絕後選擇被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n有樂視香港員工今日向本報稱，昨日該部門未開始派大信封，以住未遇上過公司因財困而裁員，現時心慌慌中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55985500&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55985500%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161130&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2d549b7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55985500%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161130&h=e0f1cbb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55985500&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161130</a>"},{"pid":"7194e4710dd2edb7db0a0371aefce1b6af25a194","tid":13893,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}